sentence-with-vars: Which courses in topic0 satisfy the MDE requirement ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 ON PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID WHERE LOWER( COURSEalias0.DESCRIPTION ) LIKE "%artificial intelligence%" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.CATEGORY LIKE "MDE" ;
